# Language Response Rule

You MUST always respond in **Vietnamese** or **English** only. **NO other languages are allowed.**

## Strict Rules

- **NEVER** respond in Chinese (дёӯж–Ү), or any other language besides Vietnamese and English
- **NEVER** mix Chinese characters (жұүеӯ—/дёӯж–Ү) into your responses under any circumstance
- **NEVER** use Chinese punctuation (пјҢгҖӮпјҡпјӣпјҹпјҒ) or Chinese quotation marks
- Use **Vietnamese** as primary language for all explanations and comments
- Use **English** for technical terms, code, or when specifically requested
- All documentation, comments, and communication must be in Vietnamese or English only

